<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q54_v14" title="Q54_v14" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una encuesta se preguntó a 100 jóvenes por el género de música que más prefieren. Los resultados fueron los siguientes:</p>
    <div>
      Género musical y cantidad de jóvenes:<br />
      Pop: 35<br />
      Rock: 25<br />
      Reggaetón: 20<br />
      Clásica: 10<br />
      Otra: 10<br />
    </div>
    <p>En este estudio, Pop, Rock y Reggaetón se consideran estilos de música moderna. Si se elige al azar a uno de los jóvenes encuestados, ¿cuál es la probabilidad de que prefiera Pop o Rock?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>80</m:mn>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La probabilidad de preferir Pop o Rock se obtiene sumando solo esas dos cantidades: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>60</m:mn>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Los jóvenes que prefieren Pop o Rock son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como el total encuestado es 100, la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>35</m:mn>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> representa solo a quienes prefieren Pop. Pero el problema pide Pop o Rock, así que se debe sumar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. La probabilidad correcta es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> representa solo a quienes prefieren Rock. Pero el problema pide Pop o Rock, así que se debe sumar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. La probabilidad correcta es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los casos favorables</strong></p>
            <p>El problema pide la probabilidad de que un joven prefiera Pop o Rock.</p>
            <p>Cantidad que prefiere Pop:
              <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cantidad que prefiere Rock:
              <m:math><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar las cantidades favorables</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>35</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, 60 jóvenes prefieren Pop o Rock.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Identificar el total de casos posibles</strong></p>
            <p>El total de jóvenes encuestados es 100.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Formar la probabilidad</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La probabilidad de elegir al azar a un joven que prefiera Pop o Rock es
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>